@CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5096

### Single user - problems for just you
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": ["Petr"]
}

### Single user with options
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": ["Petr"],
  "count": 3,
  "minRating": 1200,
  "maxRating": 1600
}

### Duplicates are handled (tourist appears twice - no problem!)
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": ["tourist", "Petr", "tourist"],
  "count": 3
}

### ONE invalid username (reports which one is wrong)
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": ["tourist", "Petr", "this_user_does_not_exist_12345"],
  "count": 5
}

### MULTIPLE invalid usernames (reports ALL invalid ones)
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": ["tourist", "fake_user_abc", "Petr", "another_fake_xyz"],
  "count": 5
}

### Error: No users provided
POST {{CodeforcesRandomizer_HostAddress}}/api/problems/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernames": [],
  "count": 5
}

###
